
Scare 1.3.10 for the Amiga
--------------------------

This is Simon Baldwin's interpreter for Adrift format text adventure games,
Scare, ported to the Amiga by David Kinder.

Adrift games can be found on the Internet: see

  http://www.ifarchive.org/indexes/if-archiveXgamesXadrift.html
  http://ifdb.tads.org/search?searchfor=system%3Aadrift

Kickstart 2.04 or higher is required.

